hisperers\" | ''[[The Whisperers]]'' || {{flagu|United Kingdom}} ||<ref>{{cite web|title=17th Berlin International Film Festival \u2013 Silver Bear for Best Actress|url=https://www.berlinale.de/en/archive/jahresarchive/1967/03_preistraeger_1967/03_Preistraeger_1967.html|publisher=Internationale Filmfestspiele Berlin|accessdate=10 December 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191223140539/https://www.berlinale.de/en/archive/jahresarchive/1967/03_preistraeger_1967/03_preistraeger_1967.html|archivedate=23 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[18th Berlin International Film Festival|1968]] ||data-sort-value=\"Audran\"| [[St\u00e9phane Audran]] || Fr\u00e9d\u00e9rique ||colspan=2 data-sort-value=\"Biches\" | ''[[Les Biches (film)|Les Biches]]'' || {{flagu|France}} ||<ref>{{cite web|title=18th Berlin International Film Festival \u2013 Silver Bear for Best Actress|url=https://www.berlinale.de/en/archive/jahresarchive/1968/03_preistraeger_1968/03_Preistraeger_1968.html|publisher=Internationale Filmfestspiele Berlin|accessdate=10 December 2017|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191223140536/https://www.berlinale.de/en/archive/jahresarchive/1968/03_preistraeger_1968/03_preistraeger_1968.html|archivedate=23 December 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[19th Berlin International Film Festival|1969]] ||data-sort-value=\"\u03c9\" colspan=\"6\" style=\"padding-left:35%\"| No Award\n|-\n| colspan=7 data-sort-value=\"\u03c9\" style=\"background-color:#EAECF0; font-weight:bold; padding-left:20%\"| 1970s\n|-\n| [[20th Berlin International Film Festival|1970]] ||data-sort-value=\"\u03c9\" colspan=\"6\" style=\"padding-left:35%\"| No Award\n|-\n| rowspan=2| [[21st Berlin International Film Festival|1971]] ||data-sort-value=\"Signoret\"| [[Simone Signoret]] (Tie) || Cl\u00e9mence Bouin || data-sort-value=\"Cat\" | ''[[The Cat (1971 film)|The Cat]]'' || ''Le Chat'' || {{flagu|France}} || rowspan=2|<ref>{{cite web|title=21st Berlin International Film Festival \u2013 Silver Bear for Best Actress|u